Solution:-
public class Solution {
    public static int isSorted(int n, int []arr) {
        // Write your code here.
           int isSorted = 1;
        
        for(int i=0;i<n-1;i++)
        {
            if(arr[i]>arr[i+1])
            {
                isSorted = 0;
                break;
            }
        }
        
        return isSorted;
    }
}

T.C. -> O(n)
